		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Goblin Caster Necklace</FONT><BR>
Zone : Halas<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD>This quest is given to you by Shamus Felligan (he
is outside the Shaman's guild).  The activation sentance is "I will hunt the
goblin casters".  The Ice Goblin Casters spawn in 1 spot in Everfrost.  They
can be found by following the right side wall after leaving the 1 guard
area.  Eventually you will come to 2 igloo's.  Casters and Scouts spawn
here.  After killing a few casters you will get either shattered caster beads, or more rarely caster beads.  Return the shattered caster
beads to Shamus and you receive faction, exp, some copper and 2 torches. Return the caster beads and you will recieve the <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=275">Gavel of Justice</A>. This
quest can only be performed by characters below level 12.<BR></TD></TR>
</TABLE>
